revision.text:
{{DISPLAYTITLE:Light_MaxNeighbor}} {{Special|234|tag|Lighting|MaxNeighbor}} * ''tag'': Tag of affected sector
Sets the light level of a sector to match the highest light level found in one of its neighboring sectors.
==Examples== {{noexamples}}
== Conversions from linedef types == The following Doom map format types can be converted as Light_MaxNeighbor: {| {{prettytable}} !Type!!Conversion!!Trigger |- |{{icon|Doom}} 12:W1 Light To Highest Adjacent Level || Light_MaxNeighbor (tag) || Player Cross |- |{{icon|Doom}} 80:WR Light To Highest Adjacent Level || Light_MaxNeighbor (tag) || Player Cross, Repeatable |- |{{icon|Boom}} 169:S1 Light To Highest Adjacent Level || Light_MaxNeighbor (tag) || Player Use |- |{{icon|Boom}} 192:SR Light To Highest Adjacent Level || Light_MaxNeighbor (tag) || Player Use, Repeatable |} ==External links== * {{oldref}}
